v.
Eusebio G. HERNANDEZ, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1641 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 26, 2017 SUAREZ, EMAS and LOGUE, JJ., concur.
